data.description: Fantastic Crystal Lake home that shows pride of ownership.  New roof in 2021.  High ceilings, brick fireplace with natural gas connection, crown molding, and genuine hardwood floors in living room.  In the kitchen that overlooks the living room, is a newer gas range and dishwasher perfect for entertaining.  The kitchen also features a microwave hood and the refrigerator stays.  Owner's bedroom suite is very inviting with tray ceiling, crown molding, and a welcoming bath retreat with large whirlpool tub, 4 foot shower, and double vanities.  The two other bedrooms are comfortably size and have generous closets. The double garage is oversized and makes a great workshop or place to tinker on your old car, hot rod, or Jeep.  Out back, is a concrete patio and a wood privacy fenced back yard.  Located close to everything!  Shopping, entertainment, dining, with easy access to Hwy 49 or I-10.  Just minutes down Canal Road to the Navy SeaBase!  Don't miss this unique home!
